Heuristica estado del mapa:

Valor por Soldado:

(allies/enemies related)
allies in range: +h_value * allies_count
enemies in sight: -h_value * enemies_count
enemies in sight/ within effective range: +h_value * enemies_count
enemies in sight/ within range: +(h_value * enemies_count)/2

(weapon related)
current ammo < fire rate: -h_value

weapon damage\ at least 1 enemy in effective range: damage * fire_rate * weapon_aff * h_value
XOR
weapon damage\ at least 1 enemy in  range: (damage * fire_rate * h_value * weapon_aff)/2


(survival related)
concealment: +h_con_value * concealment_value
remaining health: -h_health_value * lost_health




